  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research settings to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The CFD hemolysis model targets the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry and evaluates absolute hemolysis index values at Model Risk Level 5. A full 13-factor credibility assessment was conducted; seven factors were assessed with achieved levels at or above required levels, and six factors were flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all boundary condition parameters. The assessment team determined that the achieved credibility is sufficient for the intended submission context and accepted the model for regulatory use under the Minimal profile declaration. No structured Context of Use object is provided; intended-use scope is conveyed through this narrative only.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-absolute-hi-claim-001",
